{
  "stem": "19055.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a-- a rainy, cold, foggy, gloomy, gray, terrible day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very appropriate for the arrival.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They took us through those gates, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and-- and an entirely new world opened up for me, as-- as for an adult, or as for a child, or for anybody seeing emaciated people in their-- in their garbs with the stripes, and hats, and pushing wagons, and carrying tools, and-- [SIGHS] and barbed wires everywhere, and everywhere.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- The lager was sectioned to different areas, and the guard towers around it, and all over, barking dogs, the German Shepherds.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here and there, you see people beating inmates there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SIGHS] If you wanted to ask me what my feelings were, I-- I could not describe it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the end, and really, I felt this was the end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they took us to an area which was separated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were a few thousand people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Barracks, with bunk beds, three bunk beds on-- on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's where we found our accommodation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "To describe the life in Bergen-Belsen, there was a certain system.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a certain monotony of-- of life there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You had to get up very early in the morning and go outside, all the thousands of us, and stand.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Germans would call it zahlappell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They would count us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were counting us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All the time, counting us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I could never understand, why did they count us so much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If we were so valuable or-- or they just bookkeeping?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The proper German bookkeeping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The food was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was some kind of soup made of of some kind of bulbs that was to feed cows.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And parts of horses sometimes were seen in that soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The bread was made half of sawdust.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
